import { MarkGithubIcon, ThreeBarsIcon } from '@primer/octicons-react'
import { Box, Heading, IconButton } from '@primer/react'

export function Navigation() {
    return (
        <Box
            display="flex"
            bg="canvas.subtle"
            borderBottom="1px solid"
            borderColor="border.default"
        >
            <IconButton icon={ThreeBarsIcon} aria-label="Open menu" />
            <MarkGithubIcon size={32} />
            <Heading>Avocado Corp.</Heading>
        </Box>
    )
}
